OL,3,CCase of drugs mule accused Brit
OL,4,Cadjourned as family bid to clear name
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FThe family of a Teesside beautician
OL,8,Ffacing drugs charges in America say
OL,9,Fthe fight to clear her name in the
OL,10,Fcourts has been adjourned again.
OL,12,FKim Hall has been detained in Chicago
OL,13,Fsince the summer of last year after
OL,14,Fshe was allegedly caught trying to
OL,15,Fsmuggle 43kg of cocaine in two
OL,16,Fsuitcases through the city's airport.
OL,18,FThe 28-year-old says she was forced to
OL,19,Fcarry the drugs and has vowed to clear
OL,20,Fher name.
