OL,4,Cadjourned as family bid to clear name
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FA hearing on Monday (15 January) ended
OL,8,Fwith her case being adjourned until 20
OL,9,FFebruary.
OL,11,FHall is charged with the manufacture
OL,12,For delivery of cocaine, which can be
OL,13,Fcategorised as a Class X Felony in
OL,14,FIllinois, depending on the amount of
OL,15,Fdrugs involved. It can carry a jail
OL,16,Fsentence of up to 60 years.
