OL,3,CCase of drugs mule accused Brit
OL,4,Cadjourned as family bid to clear name
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FSpeaking previously to ITV Tyne Tees,
OL,8,FHall said she only thought she was
OL,9,Fcarrying cash for two men that she met
OL,10,Fon holiday who threatened her after
OL,11,Fflying her on a free trip to Mexico.
OL,13,FShe has refused to name the men who
OL,14,Fshe claims gave her the cases for the
OL,15,Fsafety of herself and loved ones.
OL,17,FFollowing her arrest, Hall was
OL,18,Fdiagnosed with bipolar disorder. She
OL,19,Fbelieves her condition explains what
OL,20,Fshe admits were "poor" decisions.
